description: Fractal Gaming Group AB engages in the provision of personal computer gaming products. The company is headquartered in Askim, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2021-02-11. Its operations devided into two segments- Cases and Other. The Cases segment includes the sale of PC cases. The Other segment includes the sale of power supply units, cooling products and fans. The firm operates worldwide.
name: Fractal Gaming Group AB
